description: Cole’s Palette is a Maryland based mobile cookery, bringing gourmet meals featuring sweet and savory waffles to a curb near you!Were a food truck unlike any other, providing a gourmet lunch experience featuring Cole’s “Sweet and Savory Waffle’s.” Cole offers a unique take on waffles, using waffles instead of bread for sandwiches. From the overflowing lump crabmeat sandwich, to the juicy and tender chicken and waffle sandwich, to the decadent red velvet waffle desert, Cole’s Palette is sure to provide clientele with the same flavorful food and appealing presentation as a fine restaurant.
name: Cole’s Palette
